<!--pages/post/post.wxml-->
<import src="./post-item/post-item-tpl.wxml" />
<view>
  <swiper indicator-dots="true" autoplay="true" interval="5000">
    <swiper-item>
     <image src="/images/1572071004386 copy 1.png"></image>
    </swiper-item>
    <swiper-item>
     <image src="/images/1572071004386 copy 2.png"></image>
    </swiper-item>
    <swiper-item>
     <image src="/images/1572071004386 copy 3.png"></image>
    </swiper-item>
    <swiper-item>
     <image src="/images/1572071004386 copy 4.png"></image>
    </swiper-item>
  </swiper>
  <view class="post-container">
    <view class="post-author-date">
      <image src="/images/1572071004386.png"></image>
      <text>Jan 28 2017</text>
    </view>
    <text class="post-title">
      小时候的冰棍
    </text>
    <image class="post-image" src="/images/1572071004386.png" mode="aspectFill"></image>
    <text class="post-content">
      冰棍与雪糕绝对不是同一个东西。3到5毛钱的雪糕犹如现在的哈根达斯，而5分1毛的冰棍就像现在的痨病鬼，时过境迁...
    </text>
    <view class="post-like">
      <image src="/images/1572071004386 copy 1.png"></image>
      <text>108</text>
      <image src="/images/1572071004386 copy 2.png"></image>
      <text>109</text>
      <include src="./post-item/post-item-text.wxml"/>
    </view>
    <template is="postItemTpl" data="{{oobj}}"></template>
  </view>
</view>
